---
// About section with photo and bio paragraphs
---

<section id="about">
  <p class="section-label" data-i18n="about-label">About</p>
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div>
      <img src="/photo.jpg" alt="Maciek Bartosik" class="about-photo" />
    </div>
    <div class="about-text">
      <p data-i18n="about-p1">
        By day I work on a large distributed backend - <strong>microservices, gRPC, GCP, observability at scale</strong>. By night I'm building TutAll, a SaaS platform for tutors, which means I think about systems from both sides: engineering and product.
      </p>
      <p data-i18n="about-p2">
        I'm an early adopter of <strong>AI-assisted development</strong> - I use Claude Code daily and actively promote that workflow across my team. In practice: faster delivery, fewer rabbit holes, better code.
      </p>
      <p data-i18n="about-p3">
        If you have a backend challenge that needs senior attention - <strong>let's talk</strong>. I work best when I can own a problem end-to-end.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-photo {
    width: 280px;
    height: auto;
    filter: grayscale(15%);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: block;
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--body);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-text p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .about-text :global(strong) {
    color: var(--heading);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .about-photo {
      width: 160px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }
</style>
